Great recipe. A trick for dealing with any unwieldy vegetable. Wash it, prick it in a few places with a knife and then put it in the microwave for about 3 minutes or until the skin softens a bit. You can then peel and cube it or cut it in half to roast - Much easier and quicker to deal with.

