Oh sweet mother of god, this is so delicious. I grow two extra plants each of sage and thyme just to get me through the fall with this soup--heaven! You can go ahead and quadruple the sage & thyme in this recipe, as far as I'm concerned... you want the texture of the soup on the thin side, because as the croutons break down, they thicken the soup considerably.

