This recipe has potential, but to my taste "4 large cloves of garlic" totally ruined the soup by taking over completely. If you make this, start with one clove of garlic and see how you like it --you can always sautee more and add it later. Otherwise you'll end up with a garlic bisque that's a pretty color.

